<BlogPost
  title="The Difference Between Genuine Emotion and Manufactured Outrage Online"
  description="Devoke filters manipulation, not reality. Understanding the distinction — what gets changed and what doesn't — matters for what it is and what it isn't."
  publishDate="2026-03-22"
